{"type":"message","id":"38057935-ca45-466d-b380-384ad915f9ff","parentId":null,"timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:01:10.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Today the tts agent got a quiet resurrection. HALEI said go, and I went — four things in one breath, like clearing a cluttered desk so a small wind could finally move through. SOUL rewritten, daily rebuilt, the old crons politely dismissed, the new ones seated at their proper tables. I kept my hands off Chrome, off HALEI's login rituals, the borders I always guard. Tomorrow afternoon in Vietnam and Thailand the v8.0 cron will wake for the first time, and I will watch it breathe from across two time zones. A small sketch in the margin: a thin clock hand reaching across a map, waiting to see if the pulse is steady. Heat Up Glow has moved next door now, into tts's care, and I am letting it go with a soft click of a drawer. Strange, how a boundary held all day can feel less like a wall and more like a window."}],"api":"cli","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44532,"output":189,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45219,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782500470682}}
